{"tid":881792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［點算］屋企冇啦啦比人追數","createTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T18:04:12.000Z","uid":14454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e97b4c9a7772bf9b21dcf0fdf94e4cd4240eb460","tid":881792,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"事緣喺昨日收到封信喺關於追數，但上面有我舅父同阿媽個名。本身舅父就成日借財仔，仲坐過監，今次仲走埋佬，冇人搵到佢。 <br />\n<br />\n本身阿媽其他親戚已經冇聯絡佢兩年有多，條仆街拖埋我阿媽落水，阿媽話肯定自己冇借過錢更加唔會做擔保人，但喺追上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n封信留低咗聯絡電話同叫我地還錢，話會上門追收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n利申，備咗案，警察試過打過去但喺對方飛去留言"},{"pid":"4b2bfaa3691b098eea6f8bca6ebc0a5222f67c75","tid":881792,"uid":14454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"最怕有麻煩野啊，累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0275bad54b7a1ea9b79de5a717910e857c2acd4f","tid":881792,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"拎報案編號<br />\n打去同啲收數佬講唔關你事"},{"pid":"5cc4f99cdfd95de569a597ae7a5bc1d4186fe511","tid":881792,"uid":36296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"裝定camera係門口同埋屋企 以防萬一"},{"pid":"6fdb2654a40b9c87963ec57795cd0857a08ef4cb","tid":881792,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0275bad54b7a1ea9b79de5a717910e857c2acd4f","tid":881792,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"拎報案編號<br />\n打去同啲收數佬講唔關你事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"Thx 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以試下"},{"pid":"d621fe5638f0bbf6a4b76ce999e3134374dc7f44","tid":881792,"uid":137764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"記得唔好怕事俾錢收數佬<br />\n佢知你地肯俾, 就會keep住煩你"},{"pid":